{"tid":1609764,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"咪撚再拎今日10.1同之前比較","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:23:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:21.000Z","uid":259519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e025db6d1c71b53e0ae2b63c1180b714effb21","tid":1609764,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">次撚次都有人出黎打飛機⋯⋯<br />\n次撚次都話勁過好過邊日又今日贏左定輸左⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街 日日都有手足傷捕 你有心情比較？我就無啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又話全民火魔？<br />\n白電油難買？<br />\n毛巾難買？<br />\n啤酒難買？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日係好左啲，會上前，但班狗衝出黎民？向後跑？如果係革命，如果係報仇，如果要對抗極權，請你保持依一刻甚至更高既仇恨，復仇！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e9cca9a8a2e53819e41d21ba2891b7592bc0db4","tid":1609764,"uid":184865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"【戰術】唔想再比人拉入嚟推Post<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609369</a>"},{"pid":"e556e427fa4a88147815217a79b84eebc67084c1","tid":1609764,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"f7ba7f9e83749c39aa968e57fb2dd17ff5f005f1","tid":1609764,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce60ecef2c367619b5b95bec27d586a3635274ea","tid":1609764,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"c